{"tid":400442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會明年3月11日補選四議席","createTime":"2017-09-14T20:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T20:05:15.000Z","uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09a96e34b4e566a1cedca8a5187050ed47600b9f","tid":400442,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:02:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】選舉管理委員會計劃明年三月十一日就四個立法會議席舉行補選。<br />\n<br />\n選管會表示，當天補選將填補四個立法會議席空缺，包括香港島、九龍西和新界東三個地區議席，及建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界功能界別一個議席。<br />\n<br />\n選管會解釋，區議會亦有補選，考慮人力資源等情況，補選需要約六個月籌備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=235986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D235986&d=qsZXs5TePvQudtD6%2FK2izo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=db01e51b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D235986&h=11b7fba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=235986</a>"},{"pid":"0db51f8ba1b8e7e81490ca23c2394a6f2e2ab2f4","tid":400442,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:05:15.000Z","msg":"換言之啫係會一次過而唔係分兩次，i guess<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然分別不大，議會一早被控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}